description:
This DLC unlocks Le Malin as a playable character, 3 new Support Ships, and additional Story Mode content for the Royal Navy's very own, Le Malin!

The Le Malin DLC unlocks the following:
Main Ship (Playable):
• Le Malin

Support Ships:
• Essex
• Baltimore
• Centaur

Story Mode:
• Le Malin - Additional Story Mode content
name: Le Malin Episode
